Product Name: CBE Carbon Monoxide (CO) 12v Caravan Gas Detector
Product Description:
CBE Carbon Monoxide (CO) 12v Caravan Gas Detector

Specifically designed for use in caravans, motorhomes, campervans and boats, the CBE 12v Gas Detector can detect the presence of deadly Carbon Monoxide (CO) in the air of your vehicle.

A toxic gas produced by combustion in a poorly oxygenated room and incomplete combustion of fossil fuels, carbon monoxide is an odourless, colourless and tasteless gas (which can often make it difficult to detect) that can leak out from faulty or poorly maintained cooking and heating equipment or tubes.

CBE Carbon Monoxide (CO) 12v Caravan Gas Detector features

  • Size: 60mm x 60mm
  • Detects carbon monoxide gas
  • Remote buzzer required

Product Name: CBE LPG Caravan & Motorhome 12v Gas Detector
Product Description:
CBE LPG Caravan & Motorhome 12v Gas Detector

Designed for use in caravans, campervans, motorhomes and boats, the CBE LPG 12v Gas Detector emits a warning noise through it’s working buzzer when activated by gas (can be disabled via the reset button).

The CBE LPG Caravan & Motorhome 12v Gas Detector has two different sensor options which can be easily selected and also adjusted for their sensitivity based on where the detector is placed and general usage of it.

The CBE LPG 12v Gas Detector can also detect soporific (A.K.A ‘sleeping’) gas which has been known in the past to be used in targeted burglaries of leisure vehicles.

CBE LPG Caravan & Motorhome 12v Gas Detector features

  • Size: 60mm x 60mm
  • Detects dangerous LPG or Soporific (‘sleeping’) Gas
  • Two different sensor options
  • Emits warning buzzer when activated by gas

Product Name: CBE PC260 Digital Control Panel Complete Kit
Product Description:
CBE PC260 Digital Control Panel & Power Management Kit

The CBE PC260 Control Panel, replaces the CBE PC200 Control Panel (Discontinued). Panel Dimensions have changed please see technical specifications below.

The CBE PC260 Digital Control Panel Complete Kit serves as the ultimate control centre for your campervan or motorhome's electrical system. This comprehensive kit provides everything you need to monitor, manage, and optimize your power usage, ensuring a comfortable and hassle-free campervan and motorhome experience.

Stay in control with the PC260 Complete Power Management Kit.

Precisely track your usage and power consumption as you safely distribute 12v/ 24v and mains power throughout your campervan to appliances, lighting, and sockets. Rest assured knowing your system is equipped with a battery charger and mains circuit breaker, allowing you to seamlessly integrate 240-volt power when connected to mains. This setup enables you to run powerful appliances and efficiently charge your batteries through your motorhome and campervan.

Never worry about a dead battery again.

The PC260 power management kit's intelligent save service battery function automatically protects your batteries from accidental drain, maximizing their lifespan and reliability.

CBE PC260 Features:

  • 3.2" Graphic Negative LCD control panel
  • Monitors car and service battery voltage and health
  • Tracks drinking water tank level (percentage and graphic)
  • Waste water tank alarm
  • Electronic battery separator
  • Controls 3-way fridge
  • Protection fuses
  • Controls car battery recharging
  • Save service battery function
  • Digital clock
  • Tests internal and external temperature
  • Twilight sensor

CBE PC260 Complete Kit Benefits:

The PC260 control panel elevates campervan life with its intuitive LCD interface. Not only does it keep you informed with system voltage and water levels, ensuring peace of mind on every journey, but it also doubles as your campsite command center. Digital clock, fridge control, and external light control are just a few of the additional creature comforts at your fingertips, making every adventure effortlessly comfortable.

Kit Contents:

1 x PC260 Control Panel (112600)
1 x DS300 12v Distribution Box (209000)
1 x CB516 12v 16a Switch Mode Charger
1 x DS120S 230v Box 25a RCD + 2 x 13a MCB
1 x Screw probes for waste water tank
1 x Cables kit for probes L=6 m
1 x Cables for control panel L=6 m
1 x Cable with sensors for internal and external temperature (L=1.5m and L=5m)

Product Specifications:

  • PC260 Control Panel - 180mm x 125mm  (HxW)

  • Distribution Box - 185mm x 144mm x 90mm  (HxWxD)

  • Battery Charger - 185mm x 140mm x 90mm  (HxWxD)

  • 230v Box - 185mm x 140mm x 90mm  (HxWxD)

Product Description:
CBE MTB Battery Tester & Electrical 4 Fuse Module with Twin Frame

A convenient module set for caravans and motorhomes featuring a CBE MTB Battery Tester and Electrical 4 Fuse Module with a twin frame.

The CBE MTB Battery Tester & Electrical 4 Fuse Module is supplied with a twin frame which is available in two different colours: Grey or Silver. Please use he option menu at the top of the page to confirm your choice of frame colour prior to purchase.

CBE MTB Battery Tester features

Ideal for monitoring the leisure battery strength of your caravan, motorhome, campervan or boat, the CBE MTB Battery Tester is easy to use and simple to read.

  • Uses no power at all when ‘resting’
  • CBE Electrical 4 Fuse Box Module features
  • Works immediately once activated
  • Features a 3 colour LED light indicator system (Charged – Green, Almost charged / getting low – Yellow, Low – Red)

CBE Electrical 4 Fuse Box Module features

Ideal for protecting four separate circuits where the user has chosen not to use an integrated electrical distribution unit (e.g. a Sargent or Zig unit), the CBE Electrical 4 Fuse Box Module can be used as a supplementary fuse board for a branch circuit (or circuits), or when the electrical distribution unit is ‘Full’.

  • 2 x 10 amp fuses
  • 1 x 15 amp fuse
  • 1 x 20 amp fuse
  • all fuses can be swapped to any rating up to 20 amps in each slot (just match your circuit to the minimum fuse size for maximum protection).

Product Name: Truma Caravan & Motorhome Awning Warmer Kit
Product Description:
Truma Caravan & Motorhome Awning Warmer Kit

To be used with any Truma Heater System, the Truma Awning Warmer Kit can be used to divert the warm air distributed by the heater system straight into the awning of your caravan or motorhome, making it ideal for use during cool mornings and evenings or during the tricky transitional periods between seasons.

This version of the Truma Caravan & Motorhome Awning Warmer Kit comes in Ivory.

Truma Awning Warmer Kit contents

  • 1m warm air duct
  • 1 x ventilator T-piece
  • 1 x shut-off
  • 1 x air outlet with flap         

Truma Awning Warmer Kit benefits

  • Suitable for connection with any Truma heating system with warm air distribution
  • Moisture reduction in awning
  • Creates a comfortable temperature beneath awning
  • Easy to operate and convenient
  • Straight forward to install (in less than an hour!)



 

The Truma Awning Warmer is suitable for connecting to warm air duct with diameters of up to 65mm.

Please note:

  • Warm air duct between heater fan and blow-out flap must be a minimum of 1.5m long to avoid overheating of the outlet.
  • When using the Truma Awning Warmer to heat your awning please be aware that simultaneous heating can reduce the heating power within the caravan.
  • Prevent the system from being penetrated by spray water by making the caravan wall as low as possible (below the main warm air duct).

Product Name: HUBi 2K Power and Lighting System Caravan Solar Hub Kit
Product Description:
HUBi 2K Power and Lighting System Caravan Solar Hub Kit

A convenient, robust and dependable energy solution for power and illumination off the grid!

The little brother of the Hubi 10k Kit, the HUBi 2k Solar Hub Kit is perfect for light to medium power usage making it ideal for lighting, small electronics and minor utilities in a wide range of settings including: caravans, motorhomes and campervans, camping trips, home and garden and backup power for home emergencies.

With five output sockets for delivering power

  • 1 x 12v auto socket capable of powering any 12v device with a mating plug and a current draw of up to 3A
  • 2 x 5v USB sockets power devices such as Smart Phones, Tablets etc. of up to 2A
  • 2 x 12v in line sockets designed specifically for the unique LUMi lighting units which are included with each HUBi Solar Hub Kit

 

HUBi 2K Power and Lighting Hub System comes with:

  • 2AH, 12v Lithium battery Solar Hub
  • 5wp, Premium Cystaline Solar Panel
  • 2.5m Connection Cable (from panel to hub)
  • Panel Stand
  • 2 x Lumi Lights with 4m cable (each will illuminate a 3m x 3m area)
  • User instructions

How does the HUBi Power and Lighting Caravan Solar Hub System work?

Daylight and sunlight are collected through a reliably high performance cystalline solar panel where this energy is then converted into DC electricity. The Solar Hub (which contains a safe and light weight lithium battery pack) of the HUBi 2k Kit then receives this converted electricity directly, featuring smart internal electronics to ensure that the system never gets overcharged and always extracts the maximum from its solar panel.

Plug and Play for a quick, easy setup

All HUBi products are designed to perfectly interconnect with one another ensuring for simplicity and a speedy setup.

With 2 handy, high quality LUMi Lights included

Each of the LUMi lights included with the HUBi 2k Kit have a brightness of 40 lumens each (capable of illuminating a 3m x 3m area) and are supplied with a 4m cable and hanging hook.

Product Name: HUBi 10k Power & Lighting Expandable Solar Hub Kit System
Product Description:
HUBi 10k Power & Lighting Expandable Solar Hub Kit System

A convenient, reliable and durable energy solution for larger power and illumination appliances off the grid!

The big brother of the HUBi 2k Kit, the HUBi 10k Power and Lighting System Caravan Solar Hub Kit is ideal for use with appliances with higher power requirements such as a 12v Television or a Laptop (Please note: The HUBi Laptop Adaptor Accessory is required to operate a laptop from the HUBi 10k Kit – sold separately).

With five output sockets for delivering power

  • 1 x 12v auto socket capable of powering any 12v device with a mating plug and a current draw of up to 3A
  • 2 x 5v USB sockets power devices such as Smart Phones, Tablets etc. of up to 2A
  • 2 x 12v in line sockets designed specifically for the unique LUMi lighting units which are included with each HUBi Kit

HUBi 10k Power & Lighting Expandable Solar Hub Kit System comes with:

  • 10AH, 12v Lithium battery Solar Hub
  • 20wp, Premium Cystaline Solar Panel
  • 2.5m Connection Cable (from panel to hub)
  • Solar Panel Stand
  • 2 x Lumi Lights with 4m cable (each will illuminate a 3m x 3m area)
  • User instructions

How does the HUBi Power and Lighting Caravan Solar Hub System work?

By utilising the natural energy of the sun via a high performance crystalline solar panel, daylight and sunlight are converted into DC electricity. The Solar Hub (which contains a lightweight and safe lithium battery pack) of the HUBi 10k Kit then directly receives this converted electricity, with smart internal electronics ensuring that the system never gets overcharged and always extracts the maximum from it’s solar panel.

Easily expandable for three times the available power

Allowing for up to three hubs to be interconnected and stacked, the HUBi 10k Solar Hub System is fully expandable meaning it has potential to provide up to three times the available power. HUBi 10k Expansion Packs are sold separately.

Plug and Play for a quick, easy setup

All HUBi products are designed to perfectly interconnect with one another ensuring for simplicity and a speedy setup.

With 2 handy, high quality LUMi Lights included

Each of the LUMi lights included with the HUBi 10k Power and Lighting Hub System have a brightness of 40 lumens each (capable of illuminating a 3m x 3m area) and are supplied with a 4m cable and hanging hook.

Product Name: PV Logic Caravan & Motorhome Fold-Up Portable Solar Panel Kits
Product Description:
PV Logic Caravan & Motorhome Fold-Up Portable Solar Panel Kits

Lightweight Foldable Solar Panels for Campervan

The PV Logic Fold-Up Solar Panels are available in a range of models including 40w, 60w, 90w, 120w, and 200w power capabilities. These foldable solar panels feature twin crystalline panels that fold neatly into a compact carry case. The 200 Watt model features 5 x 40W crystalline solar panels for enhanced power capabilities.

Perfect for travel, these compact solar panels are lightweight and highly portable, making them ideal for use in caravans, campervans, boats and motorhomes. Able to connect directly to your vans battery thanks to the inline charge controller and connectors supplied in the kit. Making this foldable solar panel great for travel, with its lightweight and portable design.

Please see the table below for more information regarding each size of panel and then confirm your choice of size using the option menu at the top of the page prior to checkout.

PV Logic Portable Solar Panel Key Features:

  • Ultra-compact inline solar charger
  • Portable design
  • Suitable for use outdoor
  • Efficient crystalline panels
  • Can be attached directly to battery via cable connections
  • Lightweight and compact
  • 8Ah Charge controller with in built diode to prevent reverse battery feed
  • High quality crystalline solar cell for 12v battery charging all year round
  • Two year warranty

PV Logic Fold-Up Solar Kit Contents:

  • Portable Solar Panel
  • Fold away support strand
  • Extension cable with crocodile clips and 12V auto plug
  • Premium padded carry bag
  • 10A charge controller with built in diode to prevent reverse battery feed (20A charge controller for 200W model only)
  • User manual and fitting instructions
  • Croc clips and 500m cable
  • Male car plug and 400m cable

Product Description:
Slimedge MHD Low Profile Campervan Solar Panel Kit

The SlimEdge MHD kit provides everything you need to easily install your solar panel and connect it to your leisure battery. Our SlimEdge solar panels are available in four sizes, ranging from 100W to 200W, catering to diverse energy requirements. Whether you need a continuous trickle feed to prevent battery drain in your caravan, motorhome, or boat, or you're aiming for energy self-sufficiency for off-grid adventures, SlimEdge has you covered.

Take Control of Your Solar Power

A charge controller is vital for any solar setup. It protects your battery from overcharging and prevents reverse current drain, ensuring a reliable and efficient power system.

Our 10A and 20A PWM charge controllers efficiently charge both 12V and 24V single or dual batteries, giving you enhanced control over your energy system. Boost Performance with MPPT Technology

For superior performance, our MPPT charge controllers can increase your solar yield by up to 20% compared to a standard charge controller. This is achieved by intelligently modifying the voltage from your solar panel system to perfectly match your battery's requirements. This means your panels will deliver maximum power with minimal electrical loss, regardless of the weather conditions.

The 15A MPPT Pro can charge dual batteries, while the 20A and 30A Pro Plus models are designed for single batteries.

Stay Connected with Smart Monitoring

All PV Logic MPPT charge controllers come with a free-to-download Bluetooth app (available on Apple and Android). This app links your smartphone to the charge controller, allowing you to easily monitor your solar system's performance, including details for your leisure battery.

Product Name: PV Logic Rigid Solar Panel Roof and Deck Top Kit for Motorhomes and Campervans
Option Set: PV Logic Rigid Solar Panel Kit
Product Description:
PV Logic Rigid Solar Panel Kit with Charge Controller

Mono High Density Campervan Solar Panel Roof and Deck Top Kit

The PV Logic Rigid Solar Panel Kit with Charge Controller is available in different wattage options to suit your needs, including 100W, 125W, 150W and 200W. This Solar Panel kits are ideal for remote off-grid travel for creating self-sufficient motorhomes, marine narrow boats, and campervans. Energy generation is maximised on the Rigid Solar Battery Kit because it includes bypass diodes to minimise the effect of shadows, maximising energy generation. Suitable for powering a range of high power consumption devices including 12V TVs and 240V appliances (when used with an inverter). Additionally, this Solar Panel Kit provides a continuous trickle feed maintain and extends to battery life of any 12V battery.

 

These Solar Panel Kits come with a 10A or 20A Charge Controller as standard. The 10A and 20A PWM Charge Controllers are capable of charging 12V and 24V single or dual batteries.

 

Upgrade to the MPPT Pro for increased solar yield by up to 20% compared to the included 10A battery controller. The MPPT Pro artificially modifies the voltage from the solar panel to match any battery requirements, meaning that this adapts to any weather conditions to deliver maximum power with minimum electrical loss. Upgrade to the 15A MPPT Pro Charge Controller for rapid solar charging. The 15A MPPT Pro can charge dual batteries, the 20A and 30A Pro Plus models charge a single battery. The MPPT chargers come with a downloadable mobile app to monitor the performance of your solar panel so you can check on your leisure battery remotely and easily just from your phone.

 

Additionally, you can custom your installation by choosing from the selection of fitting brackets including Premium Aero Brackets or ABS Corner Brackets. Select the right installation brackets to suit the needs of your campervan, motorhome, or boat!

 

Rigid Solar Panel Key Features:

  • 10A or 20A Dual Battery Charger included as standard, or upgrade to the 15A, 20A or 30A Charge Controllers
  • A choice of installation brackets available including Premium Aero Brackets, or ABS Corner Brackets
  • Water resistant and robust construction for outdoor use
  • In built diode protects against battery discharge
  • Tough and robust
  • 10-year panel warranty

Kit Contents:

  • 1 x 100W, 125W, 150W or 200W MHD solar panel with 4m cable (or 2 x 1m cable with MC4 connectors for 200W kit only)
  • 1 x 200W MHD solar panel with 2 x 1m cable with MC4 connectors
  • 1 x 10A or 20A charge controller (or upgrade to 15A, 20A or 30A MPPT charge controller)
  • 1 x premium aero bracket fitting kit (or opt for ABS corner brackets)
  • 1 x cable feed gland
  • 1 x tube elastic adhesive
  • 1 x user manual

Product Name: Fiamma A20 Universal Expansion Tank for Caravan, Marine and Motorhome Water Pumps
Product Description:
Ensure a smooth and continuous flow of water in your caravan, boat or motorhome

The pulsating water flow generated by pressure switched water pumps is replaced by a constant flow of water when you install a Fiamma A20 Universal Expansion Tank. Your water pump draws water from your water tank then pumps that water through the expansion tank. The internal pressurised diaphragm in the expansion tank eliminates any pulsating water flow and ensures a smooth, continuous flow instead, in the quantity required for showering or running a tap.

Universal use

The A20 is designed for universal use and is therefore an ideal addition to our Shurflo Trail King water pumps, previous models and all other types of pressure switch pumps. The Fiamma A20 Universal Expansion Tank is small and compact, not much bigger than a 750ml bottle of water.

Extend the life of your pump and cut water consumption with the Fiamma A20 universal expansion tank 

The universal expansion tank also saves on water and electricity, increasing the pump performance and prolonging the life of the pump, all for an outlay of around half the price of the pump. The tank builds up a head of water which under pressure comes out in a steady stream due to the internal pressurized diaphragm providing a smooth, surge-free continuous flow. The A20 can be dismantled for diaphragm operations if necessary.

Can be adapted to a multitude of pressure switch pumps

It is supplied with straight and angled 13mm flexible hose connectors and self-tapping screws for fitting. Precharged at 0.9 bars (13 Psi) the Fiamma A20 can be charged with its special valve by a normal compressor so it can be adapted to all pressure switch pumps that are on the market.

Installation Guide

Product Name: Dometic PW 3500 Motorhome and Caravan Wall Awning
Product Description:
Dometic PW 3500 Motorhome and Caravan Wall Awning

The Dometic PW 3500 Motorhome Wall Awning is built for ease of use and versatility with heavy duty retractable arms, and no supporting legs, the Dometic PW3500 Caravan Wall Awning, is always ready for use, quickly, and just when you need it!

Featuring a modern aerodynamic design, the Dometic PW 3500 Caravan Wall Awning has sizes to fit virtually any suitable vehicle, and has a high quality one piece awning canopy fabric , with no welds. Featuring an intergrated wind sensor to automatically retract in poor conditions using it's integral electric motor, the motor also features a remote control for easy opening and closing.

Please note the Dometic PW3500s are available only as a special order product, 4 to 6 weeks delivery from the Dometic factory.

*Please note it is also strongly advised to consult your vehicle manufacturer to ensure your vehicle's side wall is strong enough to fit this unsupported awning, and the loading and twisting force being created.

Dometic PW 3500 Motorhome and Caravan Wall Awning features:

  • Compact and lightweight
  • Sizes  from 2.57 to 5.01 metres
  • Ready for immediate use - extend and relax
  • Easily adjustable integrated Heavy Duty supporting Arms
  • Extremely Heavy Duty, Patented Joints
  • No supporting legs - all of the space in front of the van can be used
  • Adjustable inclination angle
  • Awning fabric made in one piece, no welds
  • Intergrated, high-performance 12-volt motor with low power consumption
  • Intergrated auto retracting wind sensor
  • Remote control opening and closing
  • Dometic weather kit as standard
  • One piece full length mounting adapter for strength
  • Full length mounting kit, including fastening materials for: Hymer, Eura Mobil and Rapido
  • Two Canopy Colours: Blue and Grey, and Three case colours: White, silver, Anthracite

The largest motorhome and caravan fridge of the Webasto Cruise Elegance line, the CR130 12/24v Compressor Fridge combines an efficient Danfoss / Secop compressor with extra thick insulation for a minimum consumption of energy and also has a 6 litre freezer compartment, two adjustable shelves, three door retainers and a vegetable bin covered by a glass shelf for tidy storage and easy organisation.

Customisable Door Panel & 6 Litre Freezer.

Please note -  Webasto fridges have a silver door panel as standard, additional panels come separately.

Quick and Easy Fitting & Secure Lock Door While Driving

With an innovative installation system for quick and simple mounting of the cabinet within your motorhome or caravan as well as a vent-lock system to keep the door securely locked whilst driving, the Webasto CR130 Fridge is perfect for use in caravans and motorhomes.

Webasto CR130 Fridge Features:

  • Volume: 130 litres
  • Quiet, highly efficient, fan cooled 12/24V Danfoss / Secop compressor (type BD35F)
  • Innovative vent-lock system
  • Easy fit installation in your caravan or motorhome
  • Ready for Isotherm Smart Energy Control
  • Blue LED internal lighting
  • Customizable door panel and handle
  • 6 litre freezer compartment with door
  • Extra thick door's insulation for low power consumption
  • Optional fixing frame
  • Webasto CR130 fridge for caravan and motorhome use
  • Two adjustable shelves, three door retainers & vegetable bin covered by glass shelf
  • Webasto fridges have a conditional 2 year warranty (see Period of warranty cover below))
  • Dimensions See Pictures

Please note that the freezer compartment is only meant for short term storage of frozen food in a mobile setting, and will only freeze to minus 6 degrees.

If a true freezer to minus 18 degrees is required, please see the Waeco CRX140

Product Name: Certikin Natural and Propane Gas Heater Swimming Pool Boiler
Product Description:
Certikin Natural and Propane Gas Heater Swimming Pool Boiler

A durable and efficient state-of-the-art swimming pool heating solution with a speedy, stress free and reliable high performance – extend your swimming pool season for longer!

Featuring a unique venting design and electronic ignition for easy, consistent performance (regardless of weather and wind conditions!) the Certikin Natural and Propane Gas Heater Pool Boiler is enhanced by an outdoor stackless top for additional weather resilience and is built to last with a robust, protective finish of anon-polluting material.

A long lasting build with a consistently high performance

Delivering more heat to your pool per unit of fuel than any other heater, the Certikin Gas Heater Pool Boiler has an intelligent build ensuring that both water temperature and flow rate are controlled inside the heater to reduce condensation, sooting and scale build-up which can shorten heater life.

Cost and energy efficient

A consistently energy smart company with high efficiency ratings, Certikin have likewise developed another efficient pool boiler gas heater which in turn can save you a pretty penny on your energy bills! For an efficient heat transfer the Certikin Gas Heater Swimming Pool Boiler also comes equipped with a unique EconTherm all-copper finned tube heat exchanger.

Certikin Gas Heater Swimming Pool Boiler features

  • Fully CE approved for most European countries
  • 80% Energy efficient
  • Special adaptor provided for PVC plumbing
  • Unitherm governor - eliminates condensation and scale
  • Easy to service and maintain
  • Resistant to wind & downdrafts
  • Can be installed indoors and outdoors
  • High wind tops for the 185, 265 and 405 models are available on request
  • Quick-fit electrics - see Pool Controller CCP04
  • Natural gas and LPG (propane) models available
  • Note - Vent kits / stackless tops are supplied FOC when ordering boiler.

*

Webasto Cruise CR49 Elegance Campervan & Caravan Compressor Fridge
Product Description:
Webasto Cruise CR49 Elegance Compressor 2 Way Fridge

Ideal for campervans & small caravans 

With its 49 litre capacity, the Webasto CR-49 Compressor Fridge is the smallest 2-Way fridge from the new Cruise Elegance line and is the ideal campervan fridge.

Customisable door panel & 4 litre freezer

Featuring an inner lining with an adjustable shelf, two door retainers and a 4 litre capacity freezer compartment with magnetic steel evaporator door, the Webasto Cruise CR-49 Elegance Compressor Fridge has optimal functionality but also benefits from extra qualities such as blue LED internal lighting, a customisable door panel and handle and extra thick door insulation for low power consumption.

230v Mains Option

The standard fridge comes ready for 12/24 volts, to add mains just tick the box, this feature will enable the Cruise 49 to operate on mains when available, and return automatically to 12/24v when no longer available.

The 230v model is manufactured in Italy with a 2-pin European plug as standard. Replacing this plug with a UK 3-pin variant or hard-wiring the fridge will not affect your Webasto warranty.

The CR49 Elegance Campervan 2 Way Fridge includes:

  • 49-litre capacity
  • 2 Year warranty (See period of warranty cover below)
  • Built-in, fan cooled 12/24V Danfoss / Secop compressor (type BD35F)
  • Vent-lock system
  • Easy fit installation solutions for a campervan or small caravan
  • Extra thick door insulation for low power consumption
  • Blue LED internal lighting
  • 4 litre freezer compartment with door
  • Customisable door panel and handle
  • Optional fixing frames
  • Dimensions DC Only 525 x 380 x 450mm Without Door, 500mm including door (HxWxDmm)
  • Dimensions AC/DC 525 x 380 x 490mm Without Door, 540mm including door (HxWxDmm)

The Webasto CR49 campervan fridge comes with the brushed stainless design door panel as standard. Pick your door colour to match your campervan or caravan interior

If you choose a different door design we'll send the standard fridge with the additional door panel you’ve selected (please use the drop down menu at the top of the page to choose additional door panel options prior to checkout).

We have a limited no. of Webasto 49 Smart Energy fridges - choose from the dropdown above

Please note that the freezer compartment is only meant for short term storage of frozen food in a mobile setting, and will only freeze to minus 6 degrees.

Please note that the Webasto fridges have a silver door panel as standard. Additional panels come separately.

Hydro-Pro 240v Inverter Swimming Pool Heat Pump
Product Description:
Hydro-Pro 240v Inverter Swimming Pool Heat Pump

A compact and energy efficient heat pump which is easy to install and simple to use!

Built from the highest quality materials (including stainless steel, PVC, and a chlorine and salt resistant Titanium heat exchanger), the Hydro Pro range of heat pumps are easy to operate and can vary the heating capacity to suit weather conditions.

With frost protection for peace of mind

The All Seasons model can operate in temperatures as low as -15°C, and features an automatic defrost function for low temperature start-ups. For additional damage prevention and efficiency, the Hydro Pro 240v Swimming Pool Heat Pump also has a winter cover included, and a soft start with no voltage peaks.

With efficient automatic controls

The Hydro Pro features new automatic heating and cooling control, allowing you to focus on relaxing in your pool. A low noise rotary compressor and variable speed fan motor ensure quiet operation, without compromising efficiency. A WiFi module is included too, for remote control. 

ECO 240v Swimming Pool Heat Pump Features:

  • COP (coefficient of performance) of up to 13
  • Automatic frost protection
  • Easy automatic control
  • Quiet rotary compressor and variable speed fan motor
  • R32 gas for environmentally friendly operations
  • Titanium heat exchanger resistant to salt and chlorine
  • Winter cover included
  • Maximum pool volume depending on average outside temperature
  • WiFi module included

Product Warranty: The Hydro Pro comes with a 2 year warranty for heat pump, and a 7 year warranty for the compressor and heat exchanger.

Hydro-Pro Type P Swimming Pool Heat Pump
Product Description:
Hydro-Pro Type P Swimming Pool Heat Pump

An energy efficient, durable and easy to use heat pump, built for longevity

Extended season heat pumps which should be installed outdoors, Hydro-Pro Swimming Pool Heat Pumps feature an oversized heat exchanger in order to maintain efficiency at lower air temperatures, making it capable of operating in ambient temperatures as low as -5°C whilst still extracting heat from the air (and as 80% of the energy produced is obtained from the ambient air then you’ll easily also save money on running costs whilst still heating your pool!).

Energy efficient (and cost efficient over time, too!)

Built from high quality materials including an ABS cabinet, stainless steel, PVC and Titanium (for the heat exchanger), the Hydro-Pro Swimming Pool Heat Pump is resistant to chlorine and salt and is also equipped with a low noise rotary compressor and fan for quiet operations. For ease of use the Hydro-Pro Swimming Pool Heat Pump has an LCD display whilst a flow switch ensures that the unit can’t run without water flow in order to prevent damage.

Hydro Pro pump features:

  • Can operate in temperatures as low as -5°C
  • Quiet operation
  • Can both heat and cool
  • Easy temperature control with integrated LCD display
  • Automatic defrost function
  • Titanium heat exchanger for corrosion resistance
  • COP (coefficient of performance) of up to 6.4
  • R410A gas for 3x lower GWP (global warming potential) over R32 gas
  • Winter cover included

How does a Hydro-Pro Swimming Pool Heat Pump work?

Very simply, Hydro-Pro Heat Pumps absorb heat from the surrounding air which then gets transferred to your swimming pool. For every kW of energy consumed by the Hydro-Pro heat pump up to 6kW of heat then gets transferred to your pool (when the ambient temperature is +15°C).

Intelligently compact for an easy installation

Note: The Hydro-Pro Heat Pump needs to be installed on a by-pass after the filtration pump (it's no longer necessary to tune your heat pump with a by-pass due to the full-flow heat exchanger of the Hydro-Pro!).

Please note: The Hydro-Pro Swimming Pool Heat Pump is available as seven different options (types 7, 10, 13, 18,22,22T and 26T). Dolphin Hybrid RS1 Swimming Pool Cleaning Robot
Product Description:
Dolphin Hybrid RS1 Swimming Pool Cleaning Robot

An energy efficient, speedy and eco-friendly suction cleaning solution for swimming pools, the Dolphin Hybrid RS1 Swimming Pool Cleaning Robot has an electrically self-powered system, using water circulation to generate electricity for its superior CleverClean scanning system which uses algorithms to ensure for the most efficient pool coverage possible.

Overcomes obstacles with precision for the quickest and most thorough clean possible

With a superior drive system for quick and precise manoeuvring around the pool, the Dolphin Hybrid RS1 Swimming Pool Cleaning Robot is capable of slope climbing and identifying obstacles such as walls, objects or drain covers which it overcomes beofre returning the robot back into its scanning patterns.  

With thorough brushing capabilities, the Dolphin Hybrid RS1 Swimming Pool Cleaning Robot is the only suction cleaner equipped with a brush which can efficiently scrub the pool floor to remove algae and bacteria. The Dolphin Hybrid RS1 Pool Cleaning Robot also features a turbine which allows for a continuous transmission of dirt through to the filter – capable of handling even rough debris to leave a clean path whilst the robot scans the pool.

Dolphin Hybrid RS1 Pool Cleaning Robot features

  • Uses minimal amounts of your pool pump's energy due it's cleaning speed
  • LED indicator signals flow rates and normal operation
  • Covers a mid-sized pool in approximately 1.5 hours
  • Suitable for pools up to 12m in length
  • Requires a 0.75hp filtration pump to run
  • Comes with a skimmer adaptor, 90 degree adaptor, automatic safety valve and flow indicator
  • Optional leaf cannister

Product Description:
Sat-Fi RV Automatic Caravan and Motorhome EU & UK Satellite Dome

The Sat-Fi RV Automatic Satellite Dome is the perfect solution for TV reception in the UK and Europe in your Motorhome, Campervan, RV or Caravan.

The latest product from CA Clase's SatFi brand, the Sat-Fi RV Automatic Caravan and Motorhome EU & UK Satellite Dome is designed with the same attention to detail as the immensely popular SatFi UK dome but with the added capability of EU use; both for Astra 2 (28E) use and for other EU satellite services.

Waterco Electro Heat Plus Swimming Pool Heat Pump
Product Description:
Waterco Electro Heat Plus Swimming Pool Heat Pump

A Summer season swimming pool heat pump, the Waterco Electro Heat Plus Swimming Pool Heat Pump is an energy efficient way to maintain a desirable swimming pool water temperature and get more enjoyment out of your pool for longer!

Featuring a robust titanium heat exchanger for a powerful heat exchange, the Waterco Electro Heat Plus Pool Heat Pump also has a weather proof ABS cabinet, top mounted fans for efficient air flow as well as a flow switch (to detect water flow and provide an automatic shut down when there is none) and auto defrost for protection against extremely low temperatures.

How does a swimming pool heat pump work?

Think of the workings of a swimming pool heat pump as being like an air conditioner in reverse - except rather than cooling they use an evaporator, compressor and condenser to extract heat energy from the ambient air and transfer this heat to the water in your swimming pool. It really is as simple as that!

Waterco Electro Heat Ultra Low Swimming Pool Heat Pump
Product Description:
Waterco Electro Heat Ultra Low Swimming Pool Heat Pump

An extended season swimming pool heat pump ideal for getting the most out of your swimming pool even in the lower temperatures of spring or autumn, the  Waterco Electro Heat Ultra Low Heat Pump has a top mounted fan for efficient air flow and a hot gas defrosting function which enables it to work when the ambient temperature is close to freezing point (0°c).

Featuring an easy to use LED control panel for simple temperature control as well as a self diagnosis system which will indicate when errors have occurred, the Waterco Electro Heat Ultra Low Swimming Pool Heat Pump also has input protection devices (auto defrost and flow switch), a robust, anti-corrosion titanium heat exchanger, weather proof ABS cabinet and provides a reliable, powerful and energy efficient performance.

How does a swimming pool heat pump work?

Very simply, a swimming pool heat pump basically works like an air conditioner in reverse. Whereas with an air conditioner the output is cool, a heat pump uses an evaporator, compressor and condenser to extract heat energy from the ambient air which is then transferred to heat the water in your swimming pool. It’s as simple as that!

Webasto Isotherm Smart energy Control Kit
Product Description:
Isotherm Smart Energy Control

Use the existing potential of your Isotherm fridge for a dramatically reduced power consumption!

If you have a Danfoss DC compressor fridge in your caravan (or are planning to buy one in the near future) then the Isotherm Smart Energy Control Kit is the perfect device to consider for getting the most out of your unit and helping you save up to 50% on energy!

The Isotherm Smart Energy Control Kit has two functions for helping you to save energy on your unit.

The first is Undercooling where so long as the running engine is feeding the battery or you’re connected to a power hook up, then chilled goods will be cooled down to +1°C. When the fridge is only connected via battery then the Isotherm Smart Energy Control Kit then adjusts the cooling temperature to +7°C so that a lot less energy is required to maintain temperature (with the chilled goods slowing down the temperature increase!).

The second is simply Energy Saver which is an intelligent control of the compressor. With this function the Isotherm Smart Energy Control Kit continuously modifies the rotation speed of the compressor depending on the requested cooling performance as well as the availability of electric power. 

Webasto Isotherm Smart Energy Control Kit features

  • Simple kit, quick and easy to install
  • Upgradability on Isotherm fridges with Danfoss/Secop compressors
  • Up to 35% energy savings solely due to compressor efficiency gains
  • Up to 50% energy savings with combined effect of cold energy surplus stored in food / drinks
  • Boost mode for quick cooling
  • Soft-start to avoid starting surges
  • No need for eutectic plates
  • Webasto Isotherm Smart Energy Control Units have a 3 year warranty

Please note: Isotherm Smart Energy Control is also available factory fitted to any of our compatible WEBASTO Cruise Elegance range of fridges.
Call us on 0151 334 0222 for more information.

Product Name: Artec Blocks Robotist Educational Transforming Robot Car Toy Building Kit
Product Description:
Artec Blocks Robotist Educational Transforming Robot Car Toy Building Kit

Build and program your very own walking robot who can transform into a car…and back again!

With the Artec Blocks Robotist Educational Transforming Robot Car Toy Building Kit, designing and building your very own robot is easier than you might think! Connect the Artec Blocks horizontally, vertically and diagonally with the option to add and remove blocks quickly from your creations whenever you want – then create programs to be transferred to your robot creation and watch your robot enact control and motion.

A child friendly robot building and programming environment free of extension boards or wires

A fantastic introduction to Arduino-based robotics programming, the Artec Blocks Robotist Educational Transforming Robot Car Building Kit features free, child friendly software with an arduino compatible board which incorporates three programming environments: A drag and drop, a simple operations based environment and an Arduino IDE.

 

 

Just connect the Artec Blocks to the plugs on the sensors, motors and Studuino board - click together, program and play!

Perfect for children to experience STEM educational experimenting first hand, the Artec Blocks Robotist Educational Transforming Robot Car Building Kit gives kids the freedom to design and build their very own robots that they can control and also customise via the accelerometer and sound, touch, infrared and light sensors.

Artec Blocks Robotist Educational Transforming Robot Car Toy Building Kit includes 140+ parts including:

  • Studuino Board
  • Servo Motor
  • DC Motor
  • Buzzer
  • LED

Product Description:

Left or right hand curved compact swimming pool slide with steps and stainless steel handrails

Product Name: Fabsil Gold 250ml Universal Fabric Waterproofer
Product Description:
Fabsil Gold 250ml Universal Fabric Waterproofer

A high strength silicone based water repellent treatment which provides an invisible barrier against rain, the Fabsil Gold 250ml Universal Fabric Waterproofer is easy to apply, colourless, odourless (when dry) and suitable for use on all fabrics!

Fabsil Gold 250ml Universal Fabric Waterproofer Features & Instructions:

  • Offers a high water resilience and is colourless and odourless when dry
  • Suitable for all fabric types
  • Extends the life of tents, awnings, canopies and bivvies.
  • Spray-on application.
  • Ensure that fabric is dry, clean and free from detergents
  • Shake well and then spray evenly from a distance of about 10-15cm
  • Should any droplets be visible on the fabric simply rub over lightly with a clean cloth to ensure penetration
  • Don't allow rain or dew to make contact with the fabric until the application has completely dried
  • Please note: May darken some fabrics.

Zodiac Ei Swimming Pool Salt Chlorinator
Product Description:
Zodiac Ei Swimming Pool Salt Chlorinator

Compact, efficient and easy to use, the Zodiac Ei Salt Chlorinator is an affordable system for easily converting your pool into a saltwater oasis!

Enjoy soft, hassle free, silky water in just 10 minutes with the Zodiac Ei Swimming Pool Salt Chlorinator which sanitises your pool water automatically so you can get on with enjoying your chlorine free pool as quickly as possible!

The Zodiac Ei swimming pool Salt Chlorinator can be installed in three easy steps (free of the hassle of getting some pipe cut!) and requires minimal maintenance thanks to its advanced electronics and auto-reversing polarity.

How does the Zodiac Ei Swimming Pool Salt Chlorinator work?

Very simply, when ordinary salt is added to the water of your swimming pool, the Quick Fix Cell of the system then generates pure sanitiser (all year round!). Once the sanitiser has finished purifying the pool water then it is reverted back into salt for the whole cycle to repeat again, making the Zodiac Ei Swimming Pool Salt Chlorinator incredibly efficient and a recycling marvel!

Zodiac Ei Swimming Pool Salt Chlorinator features

  • Easy-to-operate controls
  • Automatic reverse polarity reduces calcium buildup
  • Simple and easy to fit, 'No plumbing' installation with unique 'Quick Fix' cell
  • LCD display and LED indicators make it easy to use
  • Programmable timer
  • No flow detector

Product Name: Intex 10ft x 30 Easy Set Above Ground Pool With Filter Pump
Product Description:
Intex 10’ x 30” Easy Set Above Ground Pool with Filter Pump

Fast and easy to set up, the Intex 10’ x 30” Easy Set Inflatable Above Ground Pool is ideal as a convenient garden pool option to enjoy with family and friends on hot summer days!

How do you set up the Intex 10’ x 30” Easy Set Above Ground Pool with Filter Pump?

  • Simply fill the top ring with air, straighten out the bottom lining and fill the Intex 10’ x 30” Pool up with water! Water pressure will then cause the sides to rise.
  • When setting up the Intex Easy Set Pool with Filter Pump it’s essential that you ensure that it is positioned on perfectly level ground so that the pool fills up correctly (otherwise the sides will bow out and the water level will be lopsided!).
  • Emptying water from the swimming pool also couldn’t be easier! The Intex 10’ x 30” Easy Set Swimming Pool features a helpful drain plug which connects to a garden hose so that you can drain water away from the pool when you’re all done having fun for the day! 

Intex 10’ x 30” Easy Set Above Ground Swimming Pool

  • Intex filter pump (flow rate 1250ltr/330gal)
  • 1 x Type (H) Intex filter cartridge
  • Hose size 1.25"
  • Triple layered for extra strength

Product Name: Quick Bivvy 2000 Pop up Fishing Sports Shelter
Product Description:
Quick Bivvy 2000 Pop Up Fishing Bivvy Sports Shelter (Hydrostatic Head of 2000)

Convenient and quick to set up, the Quick Bivvy 2000 Pop Up Fishing Bivvy is a fast erect sports shelter which pops up and down in seconds! Ideal for fishing, archery or bowls, the Pop up Fishing Bivvy is a high quality shelter suitable for a variety of outdoor sports events and is perfect even in adverse weather conditions.

Why go for the Pop Up Quick Bivvy 2000?

Lightweight, easy to carry and with a handy carry bag which the Pop Up Fishing Bivvy fits easily inside when you’re all done, this tough durable sports shelter has some very handy features apart from it's speedy set up.  No need to pack the tent up if you want to move pitch, just pick it up and move it, while its still up.  You'll only need 4 tent pegs in calm weather conditions, the mini canopy still allows you to sit half in half out of the tent during rainy conditions; Keep you and your gear dry inside with the removable ground sheet and a reassuring hydrostatic head of 2000.

Quick up and down (read this!)

The Quick Pop Up Bivvy 2000 has the same technology as our original bivvy, up in a flash and down the same way (once you have the "knack"). Some customers can struggle first time, once you've got it its easy, if it's your first time with one of our fast erect angling tents we strongly suggest you watch the YouTube video below.

Quick Bivvy 2000 Pop Up Fishing Sports Shelter features:

  • Carry bag, ground sheet, guy ropes, pegs
  • Hydrostatic head of 2000 (rain resistance grade)
  • Mini Canopy that can be tied back in the event of gusty winds
  • Removable ground sheet easily attaches to tent via toggles (the tent is erected before attaching the groundsheet, and removed before taking down).
  • Rear zipped opening for pole fishing
  • Fly screen option on front door
  • W175 x D150 x H140cm, Folded size 58x  x 7 x 58cm
  • Bivvy can double as a hide

Product Description:
Thetford N4097 3 Way Caravan & Motorhome Fridge

Compact but spacious, the Thetford N4097 3 Way Caravan & Motorhome Fridge features a roomy 97 litre capacity (inclusive of an 11 litre freezer compartment) with flexible shelving, bottle slide and door bins perfect for keeping treats and essentials cool, secure and organised whilst your motorhome, campervan or caravan is on the go.

Featuring the choice of automatic or manual power source selection, electric ignition and an easy to use control panel, the Thetford N4097 is a stepped 3 way fridge freezer which delivers a high quality, reliable cooling performance with quiet operations so you’ll barely hear it even working! Additionally, the automatic model is available as a framed or frameless unit.

Please note: The Thetford N4097 3 Way Caravan & Motorhome Fridge is now supplied with a reversible hinge as standard and as such can be installed as either a left or right handed hinge. This fridge comes framed.

Thetford LED (E+) control panel:

Thetford E model fridges, which were once manual, have now been replaced with the E+ range, which are automatic, making all of the fridges in the N4000 series fully automatic. The E+ models keep things simple with a sleek and clear LED display.

 Thetford N4097 3 Way Caravan & Motorhome Fridge:

  • Stepped (for wheel arches)

  • Flexible bottle slide
  • 2 flexible white door bins
  • 2 flexible white shelves
  • Control panel
  • First class cooling performance
  • Quiet to run
  • Unsuitable for commercial or static building applications
  • Power cables and gas inlet tube at the bottom-backside of the fridge

Product Name: Smev 8821 Hob and Sink  Campervan Conversion Kit 1 + Template
Product Description:
Smev 8821 Hob and Sink Conversion Kit 1

The ideal compact kit to get your build started, the Smev 8821 Hob and Sink, Gas and Water Conversion Kit 1 is easily customisable for your needs.

Simply use the option sets at the top of the page to pick your preference between a left or right handed sink, mixer or cold tap and whether you require the kit supplied with the Camping Gaz Regulator or the Bulk Head Regulator (please see below for the full contents of what is supplied with each regulator option).

The standard Smev 8821 Conversion Kit 1 comes with:

  • 8821 Hob and Sink (Includes: seal & siphon)
  • Folding micro-switched Cold Tap or Hot & Cold Mixer Tap
  • Whale Submersible Pump
  • Two 9.5 Jerry Cans
  • 2mtr x 10mm Cold Pipe
  • 2mtr x 20mm Waste Pipe
  • 2mtr x 10mm Hot Pipe (Only available when mixer tap selected)
  • 75mm Floor Vent
  • Pack of x 5 P Clips
  • 4 x Jubilee Clips
  • Template

Supplied with Camping Gaz Regulator Option:

  • 1x Camping Gaz Regulator
  • 1x 8mm Compression Nozzle
  • 1mtr LPG Gas Hose

Supplied with Bulk Head Regulator Option:

  • 1 x 8mm Bulkhead Regulator
  • 1 x 45cm Butane Pigtail
  • 1 x Gaz Adapter
  • 1 x 8mm Straight Compression Coupling
  • 2mtr x 8mm Copper Pipe

The Camping Gaz option is for use with non-permanent installations/ The Bulkhead Regulator is for use with permanent installations.

Please Note: All permanent gas installations should be installed or checked by qualified engineer. The Gaz regulator supplied is suitable for portable units or removable pods only. For a permanent installation that complies with EN1949, please select the option which includes the Truma Bulkhead regulator.

Product Description:
Endless Summer Luxury Domestic Fixed Swimming Pool Enclosure


Designed to be the perfect cover for both free form and regular pools, the Galaxy Luxury Domestic Fixed Swimming Pool Enclosure has a robust construction in order to bear heavy loads and features an elegant, easy to handle construction designed to provide a sophisticated blend with the surrounding environment.

The Galaxy Luxury Domestic Fixed Swimming Pool Enclosure can be opened for their entire length on all sides of the pool with easy to use upwards sliding doors and special end sections. When the structure of the Galaxy Pool Enclosure is in an open position, only the supports of the structure remain on the ground so that no obtrusive thresholds or rails get in the way of people entering and leaving the pool, making them aesthetically stunning as well as gracefully practical.

Oxygen Movelite 2/2XL Motorhome Drive Away Awning
Product Description:
Oxygen Movelite 2 Motorhome Drive Away Awning

Ideal for couples, the Oxygen Movelite 2 is a compact Motorhome Drive Away Awning combining a 150 denier double rip-stop, water resistant fabric matching a lightweight and durable build alongside easy, hassle free inflation.

Featuring two oxygen air tubes and a dynamic speed valve, the Oxygen Movelite 2 Drive Away Motorhome Awning has the easiest inflation valve on the market with each air tube being capable of inflation within a single minute and for deflation to be easily achieved within the push of a button.

Perfect for use in a variety of weather conditions, the Oxygen Movelite 2 Motorhome Drive Away Awning has a light colour scheme which reflects the suns heat to maintain a cool atmosphere during hot weather, exceptional water resistance so that rain simply balls up and runs straight off the fabric and is optimised with UV protection to ensure that the material won’t become brittle or fade over time. 

Oxygen Movelite 2 Motorhome Drive Away Awning features

    • Dynamic Speed Valve (Quickest and most reliable valve on the market)
    • Intelligent Frame Relief Valve (Patented breather valve that prevents over inflation of the Air Frames)
    • Acrylix 150 Double Rip Stop Fabric (Lightweight yet durable)
    • Single Inflatable Roof Tube (Velcros easily onto the roof for extra support)
    • Vortex Vents (Help combat condensation)
    • Tintz Tinted Windows (Allow sunlight in whilst reducing glare from the sun)
    • Embossed Zip-In Curtains on Windows (Ensure privacy to the Oxygen Awning)
    • Fly Screens on Side Doors (Keep those pesky insects out!)
    • Sun Pro UV (Protects the fabric against UV rays, giving up to 3 times more longevity)
    • Endurance Storm Straps (Provides unrivalled stability)
    • Extra Wide Doors (Wheelchair and push chair friendly)
    • Rear Cowl Access Doors (Allows entry to the motorhome without having to traipse through whole drive away awning).

The Oxygen Movelite 2 Motorhome Drive Away Awning comes packaged in a smart, easy to carry holdall and comes complete with a single inflatable roof support tube, two endurance storm straps, bag of pegs and a dual action hand pump. 

Available in two sizes: Movelite 2 and Movelite 2XL

The only difference between these two is simply the height of the rear adjustable cowl with the Movelite 2 fitting motorhomes from 180-240cm (to the awning channel) and the Movelite 2XL fitting motorhomes from 240-290cm (to the awning channel).

Please use the drop down menu at the top of the page to pick your preference of Movelite motorhome awning size prior to checkout.

To ensure that you get the right size of Oxygen Movelite 2 Motorhome Drive Away Awning for your vehicle, make sure to measure from the ground to the awning channel OR measure from the ground to the roof (if you plan to throw straps over the roof).

Thetford Porta Potti Portable Camping Chemical Toilet Aqua Kem Green Sachets
Product Description:
Thetford Porta Potti Cassette Toilet Aqua Kem Green Sachets

Biologically degradable but just as effective as Thetford’s Aqua Kem Blue Sachets, these Green Sachets are an environmentally friendly septic tank cleaning option for your caravan or camping toilet.

One single sachet = one single dose

Thetford Aqua Kem Green Sachets couldn’t be easier to use with an exact single dose packed into each sachet. Mask unpleasant odours and liquefy the waste in the holding tank to reduce gas build-up, allow for easy emptying without spattering and keep the waste-holding tank clean and fresh.

Exactly enough per bag for each season

Recent research has shown that on average, campers refill the toilet waste holding tank 15 times in a season, and as a result this practical packaging (which is easy to store and lightweight to carry) contains 15 sachets to last your camping season.

Swimming Pool Competition Starting Block Podiums BCN03
Product Description:
Swimming Pool Competition Starting Block Podiums (BCN03)

Developed and patented by AstralPool for the Swimming World Championships held in Barcelona in 2003, these Swimming Pool Competition Starting Blocks feature two kep innovations:

1. It allows the swimmer to easily adjust the angle of the starting block platform by hand (available angles to pick from are 0º, 3º, 6º and 10º, within the set regulated standards of the International Swimming Federation).

2. These swimming pool Starting Block Podiums feature adjustable side handles so that the swimmer can also adjust their position easily and can be left up or down.

Manufactured using stainless steel, the Swimming Pool Competition Starting Blocks can be dismantled to enable assembly of the Omega electronic timing system and can be adapted to other systems to order. Ideal for installation in a swimming pool with side walls, this competition starting block has a platform of L550 x W500mm with a height of 437mm.

Please note: There are two types of Starting Block Podiums available, standard (with manual adjustment and fixed side handles) and Eco (fixed with no side handles), please use the drop down menu at the top of the page to pick your preference of starting block prior to checkout. 

Anchoring for installation is included.

Product Name: Artec Blocks Robotist Educational Basic Robot Toy Building Kit
Product Description:
Artec Blocks Robotist Educational Basic Robot Toy Building Kit

Build an unlimited range of robots and learn to program them to do cool stuff with the Robotist Basic kit. Build a transporter, line tracer, sensor melody light robot, arm robot car, puppy dog robot, and a sensor controlled robot - combine different sensors and motors and make up your own robotic creatures!

Artec Blocks connect vertically, horizontally, and even diagonally - build easily, and quickly add or remove pieces from your creations. Create programs and transfer them to your robot - learn how sensors measure, watch as the studuino board uses judgement and command, and the motors enact control and motion. Just connect the blocks to plugs on the sensors, motors, and the studuino board - click together, program, and play!

The Studuino is a circuit board designed for teaching programming. Designed especially for robot building, onboard connectors for the servo motor, DC motor, LED, and buzzer require no extension boards or wires when making robots. Free, kid-friendly software make this a great intro to Arduino-based Robotics programming. The Arduino-compatible board has three programming environments: a drag-and-drop, a simple operations based environment, and an Arduino IDE.

The Basic Robotist kit includes 150+ parts, including:

  • Studuino Board
  • Servo Motor
  • DC Moror
  • Buzzer
  • LED
  • Sound Sensor
  • Light Sensor
  • Accelerometer
  • Infared Sensor
  • Touch sensor 

Great for hands-on STEM educational experimenting and demonstrations, students can design and build robots that they can control. An accelerometer, sound sensor, touch sensor, infrared sensor, and light sensor let you customize your robots! Instructions included for downloading full tutorials and the robot software (requires Windows operating system). Ages 8 and up.
